---
title: Linguine in Creamy Bacon Sauce with Peas, Rocket and Balsamic Drizzle
description: This Linguine in Creamy Bacon Sauce is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/linguine-in-creamy-bacon-sauce-62e31602-431c0397.jpg
